==The Flaming Lips version==

A cover version by the Flaming Lips was included on their album &quot;With a Little Help from My Fwends&quot;, released on Warner Bros. The song, featuring vocals from Miley Cyrus and Moby, was released as official single on 18 May 2014. All proceeds from record sales go to the Bella Foundation, an organisation in Oklahoma City that helps provide veterinary care to needy pet owners.
